logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE  WHEN %1 IN ('-- Layouts: BI Publisher (XPT) layouts', 'Data Model Metadata', 'Report Metadata', 'Template File for Style Template or Sub Template') THEN '3 - Publisher Objects' WHEN %1 IN ('List Export', 'Marketing BI Data Load', 'Marketing Saved ResultSet', 'Segment') THEN '7 - Marketing Segmentation' WHEN %1 IN ('KPI', 'Scorecard Cause And Effect Linkages', 'Scorecard Causes And Effects View', 'Scorecard Custom Tree View', 'Scorecard Initiative', 'Scorecard Initiative Tree', 'Scorecard Objective', 'Scorecard Perspective', 'Scorecard Perspective List', 'Scorecard Settings', 'Scorecard Strategy Map View', 'Scorecard Strategy Tree', 'Scorecard Strategy Tree View', 'Watchlist') THEN '5 - Scorecard Objects' WHEN %1 IN ('Folder', 'Parameters: User ID, Password, Folder Path --', 'Shortcut') THEN '6 - Folders and Users' WHEN %1 IN ('Action', 'Agent', 'Condition') THEN '4 - Actions, Agents & Conditions' WHEN %1 IN ('Dashboard', 'Dashboard Page') THEN '1 - Dashboards' WHEN %1 IN ('Analysis', 'Dashboard Prompt', 'Filter') THEN '2 - Analysis' ELSE 'Other' END

CAST ( EXTRACT( MONTH  FROM %1) AS VARCHAR ( 2 ))
CAST ( EXTRACT( WEEK_OF_YEAR  FROM %1) AS VARCHAR ( 2 ))
